data.description: Welcome to this move in ready home that sets back off the road! Has 2 car garage, shed, front porch with a swing, as well as back deck for great entertaining that overlooks the view of the 20ft deep pond! As you walk into the home you are welcomed with a charming built-in bench along with a cozy dining room, & living room, with gas fireplace! A first-floor bedroom is right off the living room. The kitchen offers plenty of room to entertain & lots of natural lighting. Laundry room & bathroom right down the hall leading to a huge family room with wood stove, including sliding glass doors to the back deck. Must-see Master bedroom & bathroom with jetted tub, double sinks & shower. Upstairs has two desirable bedrooms along with an office and full bathroom. Come view this beautiful home in Andover Ohio!
